videos.description: Baylor's JaMycal Hasty rushes down the sidelines for a 41-yard gain on the first offensive drive.
videos.headline: Hasty's long run puts Baylor in red zone

videos.description: On 4th and 1, Charlie Brewer rolls out and completes a pass to Ishmail Wainright for a 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer connects with Wainright for TD

videos.description: Zeb Noland lofts a pass over the middle to Allen Lazard for a 36-yard touchdown in the first quarter. Lazard becomes Iowa State's all-time leader in receiving yards.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Noland airs it out to Lazard for TD

videos.description: Charlie Brewer tries escaping the pocket on 3rd and 17 but is sacked by Willie Harvey late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Cyclones' Harvey comes up with 3rd down sack

videos.description: Zeb Noland airs a pass down the sideline to Hakeem Butler, who pins the ball against himself with one hand and goes 67 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Butler reels in one-handed grab for 67-yard TD

videos.description: John Lovett tries rushing up the middle but Brian Peavy strips the ball for a crucial turnover in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Peavy forces red zone turnover

videos.description: Charlie Brewer tries forcing a pass into heavy coverage to Pooh Stricklin but is picked off by Reggie Wilkerson in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Wilkerson comes up with big INT

videos.description: Sheldon Croney Jr. takes the rush up the middle for a 25-yard gain.
videos.headline: Cyclones' Croney Jr. finds opening for long run

videos.description: David Montgomery rushes up the middle and takes a big hit leading to him being carried off the field.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Montgomery shaken up after big hit
